<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="about_us.css">
</head>
<style>
    @font-face {
        font-family: [Gotham];
        src: url([assets/Gothan/Gotham-Book]);
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Gotham', sans-serif;
        background-color: #422680;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #FFFFFF;
        overflow: auto;
    }

    header {
        height: 80px;
    }


    .name {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-left: 5vh;
        margin-right: 65vh;
    }

    .name .dom {
        content: url('/dom.svg');
        margin-right: 10px;
    }

    h3 {
        color: #F54952;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    h4 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 200;
    }

    .infos {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-right: 5vh;
        gap: 2vh;
    }

    .infos .home,
    .infos .about,
    .infos .contact,
    .infos .adm {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: transparent;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-left: 20px;
        font-size: 32px;
        padding: 10px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .infos .home:hover,
    .infos .about:hover,
    .infos .contact:hover,
    .infos .contact:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .infos .home .icon,
    .infos .about .icon,
    .infos .contact .icon,
    .infos .adm .icon {
        margin-right: 8px;
    }

    .main {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 50px 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 80%;
        padding-top: 20px;
        padding-left: 18vh;
    }

    h1 {
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 2vh;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    h2 {
        color: white;
        margin: 0 0 0 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }


    .sign-up,
    .login {
        background-color: #F54952;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 32px;
        width: 170px;
        height: 50px;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .sign-up:hover,
    .login:hover {
        background-color: #D43C3D;
    }

    .buttons {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        width: fit-content;
        gap: 15vh;
        margin-left: 0;
    }

    html {
        font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 300;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    a {
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    ul {
        list-style: none;
    }

    nav {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        width: 100%;

        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding: 0 0 0 3rem;
    }

    .nome_logo {
        color: #F54952;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .menu {
        width: 50%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        color: #FFF2E780;
    }

    .menu_selecionado {
        color: #ffffff
    }

    main {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .hero {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        padding-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .texto {
        width: 50%;
    }

    .texto>h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .tools {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: #341671;
        margin-top: 0;
        padding: 0;

    }

    .tools-title {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        height: 30%;
        padding: 0;
        margin-bottom: -4rem;

    }

    .seção-textoImg {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1rem 0 1rem 0;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .texto>h3 {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 1rem;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .seção-imgTexto {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1rem 0 1rem 0;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        html {
            font-family: 'Gothan', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        header {
            width: 100%;
        }

        img {
            width: 55%;
        }

        nav {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .menu {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            color: #FFF2E780;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            padding: 0 0 0 0;
        }

        ul {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .texto {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: justify;
            padding: 1rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .tools-title {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: -0.9rem 0 0 0;
        }

        .title-tools img {
            width: 1rem;
        }

        .seção-textoImg {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 0 1rem 0;
        }

        .seção-imgTexto {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 0 1rem 0;
        }
    }
</style>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="name">
            <div class="dom"></div>
            <div class="inpulse">
                <div>
                    <h3>InPulse</h3>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4>by domINators</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="infos">
            <button class="home" onclick="window.location.href='/'">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="/home.svg" alt="Home">
                </div>
                Home
            </button>
            <button class="about">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="/about.svg" alt="About">
                </div>
                About us
            </button>
            <button class="contact" onclick="window.location.href='https://linktr.ee/SuperVIZdomINators'">
                <div class="icon">
                    <img src="/contact.svg" alt="Contact">
                </div>
                Contact
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <img src="/aboutUs.svg" width="30%" />

            <div class="texto">
                <h1>About us</h1>
                <p>At domINators, we believe that a united team is capable of transforming ideas into great
                    achievements. Our mission is to promote assertive, respectful and effective communication, creating
                    an environment where transparency and collaboration are more than just words, they are pillars. We
                    were born out of the desire of a group of friends for a platform that really facilitated teamwork.
                    Today, we have brought together the main communication and organisation tools in one place,
                    providing technology companies and startups with the efficiency, agility and assertiveness they need
                    to achieve success.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="tools">

            <section class="tools-title">
                <img src="/line.svg" width="20%" />
                <h2>Our tools</h2>
                <img src="/line.svg" width="20%" />
            </section>

            <section class="seção-textoImg">
                <img src="/kanban.svg" width="20%" />

                <div class="texto">
                    <h3>Group Kanban</h3>
                    <p>The Kanban board is a method of organising tasks and the flow of activities. In the case of
                        domINators, this tool was implemented to give you a clear view not only of your activities, but
                        also those of other team members, thus ensuring better communication, as well as efficiency and
                        agility on a daily basis.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

