                </div>
            </section> -->

            <section class="seção-imgTexto">
                <img src="/mySection.svg" width="20%" />

                <div class="texto">
                    <h3>My Section</h3>
                    <p>This space is designed to give you an overview not only of your position in the team, but also of
                        all its members. This not only gives you a sense of belonging, but also gives you an overview of
                        everyone in your team.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="seção-textoImg">
                <img src="/meeting.svg" width="20%" />

                <div class="texto">
                    <h3>Online meetings</h3>
                    <p>domINators offers the possibility for the team to hold online meetings not only to carry out
                        their daily organisation, but also to hold any other meeting the team deems necessary. However,
                        the biggest advantage of this tool is that it is included in the platform, meaning that the team
                        doesn't have to switch platforms when they want to meet, they just have to create a room and
                        wait for the teammates to join.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>